- file: `smartdesk-live/src/DesktopMirrorService.js`;
- aggiunto `getSeededGoldDemoDataQuality(session)`;
- `getDataQuality()` usa lo snapshot Gold 24 mesi solo per la demo Gold compressa;
- tutti gli altri tenant continuano con il calcolo record-per-record.

Commit/deploy:

- commit preliminare seed quality: `b89c73b Raise hybrid Gold demo data quality`;
- commit fix reale Data Quality: `ab0a112 Use seeded evidence for Gold demo data quality`;
- deploy Render: `dep-d87oef9s16ns73f1k1rg`, live.

Test live:

- login `demo_gold_cockpit` OK;
- `/api/ai-gold/cockpit`: `dataQualityScore=96`;
- `/api/data-quality?summary=1`: `score=96`, `sourceLayer=seed_hybrid_gold_24m_snapshot`;
